tools.description:
Retrieve the FieldInfo for the specified field_id.

Args:
    field_id (str): The unique identifier of the field.

Returns:
    dict: {
        "success": True,
        "data": FieldInfo  # The field's information
    }
    or
    {
        "success": False,
        "error": str  # If not found, an error description
    }
